{"title":"红星闪闪（二首）","authors":["于书恒"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红星闪闪（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于书恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢洪险"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年这个时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窜出一群群野马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地图上乱闯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"践我良田，毁我村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士个个是骑手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕野性狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一兵好似一根桩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢牢夯在大堤上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军威有了高度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水位乖乖下降。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士顶天立地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手挽住黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手挽住长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水年年给英雄雕像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激流中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪高，洪水险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漩涡聚焦一个点——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个白发大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个红星闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士背着一支爱民歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激流中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个转动的光盘。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}